data.description: With over 2000 sqft (finished & unfinished) this 3 bedroom, 2 bath ranch style house sits on a corner lot in the Ridge Creek subdivision. The covered front porch leads to a living room w/new laminate floors. The kitchen & dining area features ceramic tile floors, lots of honey oak cabinets, breakfast bar, & stainless steel appliances! The carpeted master bedroom has a tray ceiling w/fan & recessed lights & 8’x6' WIC. The attached master bath features a tiled shower/jetted tub, ceramic tile floors, & double vanity. There are two more guest bedrooms w/ceiling fans (1 w/arched window & laminate flooring) & a full guest bathroom w/ceramic tile floors. Other features of this house includes a 25’x26' garage with 13’ ceilings & workbench, a large privacy fenced back yard, large back deck & a shed. Living room & garage are wired for surround sound. Home network is also included w/camera unit. Call to schedule a showing today! The garage refrigerator, freezer, & toolbox not included.
